Jadi sekarang EMM kan punya GHL , jadi Enterprise (saat ini hanya EMM) bisa konek ke GHL lalu tiap kali agency daftar kita bisa insert ke kontak dan tambahin Tag setiap action yang dilakukan agency tersebut:

1. "account-created" tag is added as soon as their account is created, through either the front end, or back end, and before they agree to the terms of service. ✅
2. "agreement-signed" tag is added when the agree to the terms of service and successfully pay the onboarding fee. ✅
3. "stripe-connected" when they connect stripe. (nanti)
4. "whitelabel-setup" is added when they have "True" for Status Domain and also Status SMTP
5. "campaign-started" is added when they have at least one campaign started ✅
6. "over-min-spend" is added whenever they pass their monthly anniversary over minimum spend (progress)
7. "under-min-spend" is added whenever they pass their monthly anniversary under minimum spend 
8. "manual-bill-enabled" is added If Status Manual Bill is True ✅
